column5: Anyone going to this?I will be there [ice Permitting] along with 4 Friends...

Pretty anxious to see the results of this derby.  I fished there alot before it iced up, and no action was happening at all there.  And I mean no action!  Hopefully some more fished moved in over the winter, or else it'll be a tough fishing day. Good luck to all going out.
I'll be there. Should be a fun day, even if no fish.
